## Key Takeaways

To quickly identify which sources AI Overviews prioritize for a specific query, paste the results into a separate AI model and ask it to "Extract the citations and rank them by order of appearance." This bypasses manual scanning and immediately reveals which domains the search engine considers most authoritative for that topic.

